# compiled binary (zig build-exe emits ./main)
/main

# ad-hoc scratch binaries from `zig run`/build-exe at the repo root (review agents
# leave these behind; keep them out of `git add -A`). Both name orders, since an
# agent compiled `nyra_test` (suffix) past the `test_*` (prefix) rule once.
/test_*
/*_test
